 The plant is subject to the pricing provisions of a State-operated
milk pricing plan which provides for the payment of minimum class
prices for raw milk;

 Receives no fluid milk products, and acquires no fluid milk
products for route disposition, from sources other than own farm
production;

 In any month, not less than 10 days' production of the
producer whose milk is diverted is physically received at a pool
plant during the month;

